snippet.title: Jussie Smollett, LGBTQ in Hollywood, Boosie, & Johnny Depp Framed by Amber Heard || RAW Cognizance
snippet.description:
This is a snippet from Episode 3 of RAW Cognizance Podcast featuring our special guest, Brandon "Beezy" Anderson. It includes a discussion on Jussie Smollet, Boosie, and Johnny Depp Framed by Amber Heard. Listen to the full episode today!

Download the podcast today: https://plinkhq.com/i/1590021425
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/show/6d9seomKa39zm9Atwi40PW
Apple: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/raw-cognizance/id1590021425

FOLLOW US ON SOCIAL MEDIA:
RAW Cognizance Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RAWCognizance
Alex's Twitter: https://twitter.com/JustAlyxCentral
Alex's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ahix717/
Alex's Original YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/JustAlyx

Welcome to RAW Cognizance. A podcast that discusses all the fun topics authentically and all the fundamental topics in a fun way. No matter what happens --, you'll always get the real deal. 

Shout out to Houston Podcast Studio for the support and opportunity to make this happen.

#RAWCognizance #JohnnyDepp #Boosie
